46
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:01,520
Xiao...

47
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:02,280
Ci'er,

48
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,600
this time,

49
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,960
