79
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:28,240
Let go of me!

80
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,680
Xiao Che, you maniac!

81
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,960
Let go of me!

82
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:03,000
Let go of you?
Don't even think about it.

83
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,760
Xiao Che, you maniac!

84
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:35,000
Jiang Jinli, how dared you

85
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:36,480
to poison me!

86
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,520
What are your dirty secrets

87
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:43,000
about trying to kill me?

88
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:50,160
I hurt you accidentally
yesterday to protect myself.

89
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:52,160
I didn't want to kill you,
Your Highness.

90
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:55,608
Instead, do you remember

91
00:09:55,632 --> 00:09:57,480
when you were drunk yesterday...?

92
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:00,600
What happened? Tell me.

93
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,400
Yesterday when you were drunk,

94
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,440
you mistook me for the Empress.

95
00:10:06,771 --> 00:10:08,390
You have fantasies
of your sister-in-law...

96
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,000
Shut up!

97
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,880
Be careful with your words.

98
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,280
The Empress has always behaved so well.

99
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:17,080
For the Emperor
and the consorts, she is flawless.

100
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,760
She is not the one
you can fantasize about.

101
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:23,840
Just for spreading rumors,

102
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:29,080
I can punish you
for disrespectful behaviors.

103
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:31,560
Qing Yi.

104
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,080
Yes.

105
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,440
(He cares so much about me.)

106
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,714
(Was it really him in the first place?)

107
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:50,440
(Then who killed me?)

108
00:10:51,657 --> 00:10:53,857
(I wonder when His Majesty
will return to the palace.)

109
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:57,160
(I have to meet His Majesty
to investigate this matter.)

110
00:10:58,171 --> 00:10:59,310
Find out as soon as possible

111
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,520
if Princess Consort is related
to the death of the Empress.

112
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:01,880
Yes.

113
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:06,040
After releasing Xue Lian,

114
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:08,360
did anyone contact her in private?

115
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,240
After she was released,

116
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:12,160
she locked herself
in her room all the time.

117
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:13,600
Our men are monitoring day and night

118
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,942
but have yet to discover anything.

119
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:17,960
Princess Consort seems to have no idea
of Xue Lian's disappearance.

120
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:20,240
Keep on monitoring.

121
00:11:22,028 --> 00:11:22,920
Yes, Your Highness.

122
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:32,280
